# Setup

Configure your game's mathematical foundation.

- [Game Config](/docs/math-sdk/setup/configs) - GameConfig parameters, reels, paytable, and symbols
- [Bet Mode](/docs/math-sdk/setup/betmode) - Max win, RTP, cost multiplier, and distributions
- [Distribution](/docs/math-sdk/setup/distribution) - Win criteria, quotas, and force conditions
